Dear {!Contact.FirstName},
We hope you enjoyed the session A to Z's of Written Policy Requirements presented by Martie Adler. Attached you will find the handout from the session which can be used as a guide as you are reviewing regulatory compliance and a summary of the changes that impact written policy requirements as a result of the reauthorization of the Higher Education Act.
If you should have any questions about this session or other trainings offered by American Student Assistance, please feel free to e-mail your regional account executive. If you are not familiar with the representative for your institution you can e-mail our team at teamnewengland@amsa.com and either Tanya Tanaro, Jeff Bentley or Wesley Alston will respond.
Thanks for attending the A to Z's of Written Policy Requirements!
Sincerely,
Tanya, Jeff and Wesley
